bottler
-------
Simple irc bot made in C.
Currently it can join, part and fetch url titles.
Configuration is done by editing config.h and rebuilding.
You can also pass options via commandline parameters.

usage
-----
usage: bottler [options]

-h    help
-v    version

-s <host>       server hostname
-p <port>       server port
-n <nick>       bot nickname
-u <name>       bot username
